"{\"uid\": \"awfulannouncing.com-olympics-simone-biles-criticizes-media-questions-future.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Awful Announcing  Everyone wonders what's next for Simone Biles.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 64, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Will she return for another Olympics in 2028?\", \"from\": 66, \"to\": 111, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Or is she capping her incredible career in the Paris Olympics?\", \"from\": 112, \"to\": 174, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"There is plenty of time for Biles to decide her future plans.\", \"from\": 176, \"to\": 237, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She just does not want to talk about her decision immediately following a gold medal-winning event in Paris.\", \"from\": 238, \"to\": 346, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 340, \"end\": 345, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.4449604147803035e-14, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The gymnast posted a couple of messages on X Sunday morning, chiding reporters who ask her, or any athlete, \\\"what's next?\\\"\", \"from\": 348, \"to\": 470, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"right after a winning performance.\", \"from\": 471, \"to\": 505, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"you guys really gotta stop asking athletes what's next after they win a medal at the Olympics  - Simone Biles (@Simone_Biles)August 4, 2024    let us soak up the moment we have worked our whole lives for  - Simone Biles (@Simone_Biles)August 4, 2024    It's understandable that reporters want to ask a question that everyone is wondering.\", \"from\": 507, \"to\": 845, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Yet Biles spoke for many athletes who find themselves faced with similar questions under similar circumstances.\", \"from\": 846, \"to\": 957, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Let the athletes celebrate their achievement in the moment.\", \"from\": 958, \"to\": 1017, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Fans had plenty of fun with Biles' posts.\", \"from\": 1019, \"to\": 1060, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"One fan asked \\\"What is your next step after winning Gold medal??\\\"\", \"from\": 1061, \"to\": 1126, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Biles responded, \\\"Babysitting the medal.\\\"\", \"from\": 1127, \"to\": 1168, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"What is your next step after winning Gold medal??\", \"from\": 1170, \"to\": 1219, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"- Malkia Nyuki \\ud83d\\udc51 (@nyuki_malkia)August 4, 2024    babysitting the medal  - Simone Biles (@Simone_Biles)August 4, 2024    For any athlete who wants to prank the media with an off-the-wall response to such a question, fans had plenty of suggestions.\", \"from\": 1221, \"to\": 1468, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Repeat this for all life milestones please:  \\\"Congrats on your wedding, when are you having a baby?\\\"\", \"from\": 1470, \"to\": 1570, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Congrats on your baby, when are you having another baby?\\\"\", \"from\": 1572, \"to\": 1630, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Let people revel in something for a while before moving on to what's next  Congrats on this Olympics!\", \"from\": 1632, \"to\": 1733, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You are#TheGOAT  - Peep Peep (@peeppeeparoo)August 4, 2024    \\\"i am goin to disneyland!\\\"\", \"from\": 1734, \"to\": 1822, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"a time honored response  - David Goldfarb (@locust9)August 4, 2024    You should just have some really crazy answers ready:  \\\"I am gonna climb Mount Everest with a blindfold on.\\\"\", \"from\": 1823, \"to\": 2001, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am going to buy Nebraska.\\\"\", \"from\": 2003, \"to\": 2032, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2023, \"end\": 2031, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nebraska_Cornhuskers\", \"scor